name: adam kim
text: Great group of people to work with from both a technical and personal standpoint

name: Jerome Taylor
text: I got here the night before appt. Was able to pull around back of building to rest. Forklift driver told me which door to back into at 0400 because he said it would get real busy come morning. The morning crew was curios as to why I didn't get unloaded the night before. I expect confusion just starting a new account, no problem they unloaded me right away. Parking, and docking are tight due to employees parking illegally.

name: Renee Prince
text: We were loaded quickly even though we were there a few hours early for pick up.  Employees were very nice.

name: Bran Higginsgrttg
text: Great People work there! They load my truck in a Very Timely manner and get me on to my next pick up.

text: No one knows his bud from his elbow. Nazis like to hire low wage slaves who dont give a s*****. Mercedes picks up half of their machines. Germans are so naive with mamagement abilities of a bucked of sand. All 4 and 5 star ratings are employees asked to do so by management.

name: Joey Anderson
text: Getting in and out of here is a nightmare when the OTR trucks come in and park all over the place.  Looks like they should be able to figure out where to park so another big rig can get to the dock.  SMH.
